### EDA: Calculate descriptive statistics of your choice
```{r}
durationsGe %>%
  summary()
```
```{r}
durationsGe %>% 
  group_by(Sex) %>% 
  summarise(
    MeanSpeechRate = mean(SpeechRate),
    DurationOfPrefix = mean(DurationOfPrefix))

```

```{r}
durationsGe %>% 
  mutate(
    Newdata = mean(SpeechRate),
    DurationOfPrefix = mean(DurationOfPrefix))
```


